text: Roush Fenway Racing is a NASCAR team owned by Jack Roush and John W. Henry. This team owns race cars that race in the NASCAR Sprint Cup, Nationwide Series, Camping World Truck Series, and the ARCA RE/MAX Series. Roush Fenway Racing has won two Sprint Cup championships with Kurt Busch and Matt Kenseth. Category:NASCAR racing teams
title: Roush Fenway Racing
